title: 'SCAN_GENERATED_PLIST_FILE ' lane context is nil with Xcode 10 Beta 5
body:
### New Issue Checklist - [x] Updated fastlane to the latest version - [x] I read the [Contribution Guidelines](https://github.com/fastlane/fastlane/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md) - [x] I read [docs.fastlane.tools](https://docs.fastlane.tools) - [x] I searched for [existing GitHub issues](https://github.com/fastlane/fastlane/issues) ### Issue Description The `run_test` action does not generate `SCAN_GENERATED_PLIST_FILE` lane context with Xcode 10 Beta 5. Then, [trainer](https://github.com/KrauseFx/trainer) plugin does not work. Fastfile ``` run_tests(scheme: scheme, code_coverage: true, fail_build: false) puts "== Run Test Lane Contexts ==" p lane_context[Actions::SharedValues::SCAN_GENERATED_PLIST_FILES] p lane_context[Actions::SharedValues::SCAN_GENERATED_PLIST_FILE] ``` will produce... Xcode 10 Beta 5: ``` == Run Test Lane Contexts == [] nil ``` Xcode 9.4.1 ``` == Run Test Lane Contexts ["/Users/tahori/Library/Developer/Xcode/DerivedData/sample_calc_v2-azembgmojnserpaxnpohmrdaamsu/Logs/Test/AE86324F-E4AD-4D57-BBE8-81917015C34D_TestSummaries.plist"] "/Users/tahori/Library/Developer/Xcode/DerivedData/sample_calc_v2-azembgmojnserpaxnpohmrdaamsu/Logs/Test/AE86324F-E4AD-4D57-BBE8-81917015C34D_TestSummaries.plist" ``` ##### Complete output when running fastlane, including the stack trace and command used
